Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大海!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,的前夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,兴致高涨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,花名 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,看表情好像是有心事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不会游泳所以害怕海?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的 小花名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在海边相互追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在沙滩写下「love」然后让海浪冲刷掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 但是 不是这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要穿比基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.67,0:00:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想到要露出肚脐就紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,多露出点反而显得身材好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说的话全裸不就是最强了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,露出肚脐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 现在就睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,明早还要早起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,荣依子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,去到了海边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可以在荣依子你的身体上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.26,0:01:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,倒满白色的滑溜溜的液体然后涂个遍可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好
